00:04:17,007 --> 00:04:20,350
who wouldn't recognise true genius if
it was standing in front of them giving a speech.
就算一个真正的天才在面前讲演
他们也绝对察觉不到

65
00:04:21,409 --> 00:04:22,975
Which if I were there, would be.
如果我在那儿的话 就会这样的

66
00:04:24,289 --> 00:04:25,426
I don't know Sheldon.
我不明白 Sheldon

67
00:04:25,427 --> 00:04:28,801
Those topical conferences on
Bose-Einstein condensates' parties are legendary
玻色-爱因斯坦凝聚体主题会的
派对可是传奇性的啊!

68
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:33,058
- Forget the parties!
- Forget the parties? What a nerd.
- 别提那些派对了!
- 别提那些派对了? 书呆子!

69
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:37,735
Are there any other honours I've got that I don't know about?
还有其他我不知情的荣誉吗?

70
00:04:37,855 --> 00:04:40,669
