00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:43,933
Leonard, please don't take this the wrong way,
but the day you win a Nobel prize,
Leonard 请别误会
但是什么时候你能得诺贝尔奖

72
00:04:44,053 --> 00:04:48,133
is the day I begin my research on the drag coefficient of tassles on flying carpets.
我就什么时候开始对
飞毯流苏的药物共作用性研究

73
00:04:50,450 --> 00:04:52,987
the only thing missing from that insult was: "your mama".
这个羞辱只漏了一点 就是"你妈妈"

74
00:04:54,773 --> 00:04:55,766
I got one...
Hey Leonard,
我有个...
嗨 Leonard

75
00:04:55,886 --> 00:04:59,190
- Your mama's research methodology is so flawed...
- Shut up, Howard.
- 你妈妈的研究方法论也太次了...
- 闭嘴 Howard

76
00:05:00,483 --> 00:05:02,812
- Sheldon, we have to do this.
- No, we don't.
- Sheldon 我们必须去
- 不 没必要

77
00:05:02,867 --> 00:05:05,210
We have to take a nourishment, to expel waste,
我们必须摄取营养 排泄废物

78
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:07,869
and inhale enough oxygen to keep our cells from dying.
吸取足够的氧气来保持细胞活性

79
00:05:07,951 --> 00:05:09,376
Everything else is optional.
剩下的都是可选的

80
00:05:10,421 --> 00:05:12,449
Ok, let me put it this way:
I'm doing it.
好吧 我这么说吧
我要去

81
00:05:12,531 --> 00:05:14,779
